  "description": "Tabla×2 with harmonic tuning, Mridangam-like Tabla (artic=1, edge/rim), Doumbek in kanjira role. 5 active seats, straight time, Carnatic rhythmic logic at sunrise tempo.",
  "tags": [
    "aether",
