  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Natya Shastra (Bharata Muni): 'The tala is the ocean; the solkattu are its waves'",
      "Carnatic teaching: 'Laya is not tempo — laya is the living breath of time'",
      "Tyagaraja, Endaro Mahanubhavulu: 'How many great beings — salutations to all'"
    ],
    "revelation": "The Flock's Feather revealed: Tabla harmonic modes emerge when you layer two Tabla voices tuned a perfect fourth apart (0 and +5 semitones), then add the edge articulation as the chatusra nadai counter-melody. The doumbek fills the kanjira role — the small voice that holds the felt beat.",
    "god": "Feather",
    "flock_note": "The Pulse noted: swing=0.0 is mandatory for Carnatic — the Western ear mistakes this for stiffness, but it is precision as spiritual practice. Any swing destroys the tala architecture.",
    "diagnosis": "Carnatic Dawn asks the drum to become mathematics — and discovers that mathematics, at dawn, sounds like prayer."
  },
